WEBVTT

09:09.260 --> 09:11.320 line:80%
She'd hit my left hand, then my right.

09:11.920 --> 09:12.670 line:80%
She was heavy-handed.

09:12.670 --> 09:13.960 line:80%
It really hurt.

09:14.120 --> 09:15.680 line:80%
But every time she finished,

09:15.680 --> 09:18.080 line:80%
she'd still buy candy
for Changning and me.
